{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"算法","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Algorithm","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>算法是一个良定义的具体计算步骤的一个序列。</p>\n<p>换句话说，一个算法就是由人或机器可重复的解决问题的方法。计算机科学家们使用算法的复杂度（又称 O 标记法）来表示算法的效率。</p>\n<p>例如：</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>一道菜谱就是供人使用的算法</li>\n  <li>一种编程中常用的排序算法就是用来描述计算机如何给数据排序的</li>\n</ul>\n<p>常用的算法有寻找最优路径算法，例如“旅行推销员问题”、“树的遍历算法”等。</p>\n<p>还有很多机器学习算法例如“线性回归”、“决策树”、“随机森林”、“支持向量机”、“循环神经网络（RNN）”、“长短时记忆（LSTM）神经网络”、“卷积神经网络（CNN）”、“深度卷积神经网络”等。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"更多详情","title":"更多详情","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"通用知识库（维基百科）","title":"通用知识库（维基百科）","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Algorithm\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Algorithm</a>，维基百科</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"技术分析","title":"技术分析","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.toptal.com/developers/sorting-algorithms\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Explanations of sorting algorithms</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://bigocheatsheet.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Explanations of algorithmic complexity</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"更多详情","id":"更多详情"}],"summary":"算法是一个良定义的具体计算步骤的一个序列。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Algorithm","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Algoritmo","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Algorithme","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Algorithm (アルゴリズム)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Algorithm","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Algoritmo","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Алгоритм","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"演算法","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/algorithm","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-con